# 15 - Travel Planner
# Create detailed travel itineraries

NAME travel-planner
INPUT destination
INPUT duration DEFAULT "7 days"
INPUT interests DEFAULT "culture, food, nature"
INPUT budget DEFAULT "moderate"

GOAL research "Research $destination: attractions, neighborhoods, local customs, best times to visit, and hidden gems matching $interests."
GOAL logistics "Plan logistics: suggested areas to stay, transportation options, and $budget budget breakdown."
GOAL itinerary "Create a day-by-day $duration itinerary balancing $interests with practical considerations like travel time."
GOAL tips "Add practical tips: packing list, local phrases, safety notes, and booking recommendations. Save the complete travel plan to travel-plan-output.md."

RUN plan USING research, logistics, itinerary, tips
